---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 1, 2024';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms and Conditions | Beautyflow Beauty Salon"
  description="Beautyflow Beauty Salon's terms and conditions. Learn about the conditions for using our services."
  lang="en"
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#fdf8f6] via-white to-[#f8f4f9]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase text-center font-bold">
        Terms and Conditions
      </h1>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">1. Service Provider</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Company name:</strong> Beautyflow Kft.<br />
            <strong>Address:</strong> 1116 Budapest, Fegyvernek utca 121., Hungary<br />
            <strong>Tax number:</strong> 32724316-1-43<br />
            <strong>Company registration:</strong> 01-09-439280<br />
            <strong>Email:</strong> hello@beautyflow.pro<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> +36 1 300 9414
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">2. Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Beautyflow Beauty Salon provides the following cosmetic and beauty services:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Diode laser hair removal</li>
            <li>Permanent makeup (eyebrows, lips, eyeliner)</li>
            <li>Laser tattoo removal</li>
            <li>Carbon Peeling facial treatment</li>
            <li>HydraBeauty facial treatment</li>
            <li>Pigmentation removal</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">3. Booking</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Appointments can be booked via the Notino.hu platform, by phone, or in person.
            Upon confirmation, the appointment is considered final.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">4. Cancellation Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Appointments may be cancelled free of charge up to <strong>24 hours</strong> before
            the scheduled treatment. Late cancellations or no-shows may incur a charge of
            50% of the treatment price.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Please notify us of cancellations by phone (+36 1 300 9414) or email (hello@beautyflow.pro).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">5. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Payment methods:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Cash</li>
            <li>Debit/Credit card (Visa, Mastercard)</li>
            <li>SZÃ‰P card (Hungarian benefit card)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            Payment is due on-site after the treatment is completed.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">6. Health Requirements</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Certain treatments require health eligibility.
            Please consult with us in advance if you have any of the following conditions:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Pregnancy or breastfeeding</li>
            <li>Skin conditions (eczema, psoriasis)</li>
            <li>Diabetes</li>
            <li>Medication use (especially photosensitizing drugs)</li>
            <li>Active infections or inflammation</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">7. Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            The service provider is not liable for damages resulting from undisclosed health
            information by the client or failure to follow post-treatment care instructions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">8. Complaints</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            You may submit complaints via email at hello@beautyflow.pro or by phone at +36 1 300 9414.
            We will investigate your complaint within 30 days and respond in writing.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase font-bold">9. Final Provisions</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Matters not regulated in these Terms and Conditions are governed by the Hungarian
            Civil Code and applicable Hungarian law. The service provider reserves the right
            to modify these terms, which become effective upon publication on the website.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a
          href="/en/"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#c53f75] text-white font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide rounded-full hover:bg-[#a33460] transition-colors"
        >
          Back to Homepage
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
